note: Vaylufa was born in the bustling neon-lit metropolis of NeoTokyo in the year 2157. Growing up in a world dominated by advanced technology and cybernetic enhancements, she developed a deep fascination for the fusion of humanity and machines. From an early age, Vaylufa immersed herself in the realm of anime and video games, finding solace and inspiration in their imaginative and virtual worlds.
